File: plugins/e2e-test/src/tools/sdk-remove-storage.ts

Current code imports getLocalStorage and getSessionStorage from the SDK but reimplements removal logic inline (lines 30-38) with a try/catch around localStorage.removeItem / sessionStorage.removeItem. The stale comment at lines 7-11 incorrectly states the SDK doesn't export removeLocalStorage/removeSessionStorage.

The SDK exports both at platform/plugin-sdk/src/index.ts lines 330 and 335:
  export { removeLocalStorage } from './storage.js';
  export { removeSessionStorage } from './storage.js';

Fix: Add removeLocalStorage and removeSessionStorage to the import from @opentabs-dev/plugin-sdk. Replace the inline try/catch block with calls to the SDK utilities. Remove the stale JSDoc comment.
